snippet.description:
Pocket Shooter Hardcore - Funny emoji pop shooter game. Mad Emojis arrive and prepare to invade earth. Hard times have only just begun. Bullet Boy is the only brave but frenzy super Hero who can resist and protect the planet. Grab the gun and stop this frenzy war now!
